    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>To add Displacement to your geometry, you first need to set up a material network with a PxrDisplace as shown <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544644642/Using+Displacement\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>, and once done, you will also need to add displacement settings to the geometry.</p><p>These parameters can be found under RenderMan &gt; Prototype Attributes &gt; Shading &gt; Displacement and at a minimum, primvars:displacementbound:sphere needs to be set &gt; 0. </p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"997\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640621/RenderMan_Displacement.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078350&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=997&amp;height=548\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640621/RenderMan_Displacement.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078350&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"548\" data-width=\"997\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640635\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Displacement.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640621\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ed351850-c94a-4c7b-8453-c576400cc897\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640621/RenderMan_Displacement.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078350&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=997&amp;height=548 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640621/RenderMan_Displacement.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078350&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=997&amp;height=548 1x\"></span><p /><p>If tearing occurs, select Smooth Normals and Smooth Displacement under Prototype Attributes &gt; Geometry &gt; Polygon. </p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"997\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640621/RenderMan_Displacement_Dicing.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078350&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=997&amp;height=801\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640621/RenderMan_Displacement_Dicing.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078350&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"801\" data-width=\"997\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640638\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Displacement_Dicing.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640621\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"131883a8-521f-4ca8-925a-ff9eb7f70749\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640621/RenderMan_Displacement_Dicing.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078350&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=997&amp;height=801 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640621/RenderMan_Displacement_Dicing.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078350&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=997&amp;height=801 1x\"></span><p />"
    }
